            Read more on docs &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
          <h5 class="d-inline-block lh-base">
            <i class="align-middle bi bi-bar-chart-line-fill fs-4 me-2 text-primary"></i>

            Simple analytics, user-friendly reports
          </h5>

          <div>
            Simple, clear and easy to understand reports, without overwhelming you with unnecessary details. Whether you're a beginner or an
            experienced data analyst, you'll appreciate the clarity of our reports.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
          <h5 class="d-inline-block lh-base">
            <i class="align-middle bi bi-shield-fill-check fs-4 me-2 text-primary"></i>

            100% data ownership
          </h5>

          <div>
            You have complete ownership of your data. There's no behavioral marketing or surveillance capitalism, giving you peace of mind
            that your privacy is being protected.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
          <h5 class="d-inline-block lh-base">
            <i class="align-middle bi bi-clipboard-data-fill fs-4 me-2 text-primary"></i>

